Behavioral reference
--------------------
Dombra is an independent implementation. Its feature set and user-facing
behavior are modeled after Cosmos Music Player for iOS
(https://github.com/clquwu/Cosmos-Music-Player, GPL-3.0). No source code
from Cosmos Music Player has been copied or translated into this project;
it served as a behavioral reference only.
